Text:
(Now that I have Yukime's seal of approval on the
counterfeiting plan, there's nothing left for me to
do but wait for her to print the fake bills.)

(Once that happens, my job'll be taking out enemy
spies so they can't figure out where the counterfeits
are coming from.)

(The mysterious man, John Smith, who pulls strings
from behind the scenes, as Mitsugoshi and the MCA
wage war out in the open.)

(I'm a Super Elite Agent who must betray his
organization...)
Boss man, you smell like fox.
Uh, I was hanging out—I mean, foxhunting.
Sorry, but the foxes are all hunted up.
Also, could you get off me now?
Delta, what are you doing in the capital?

I woke up early this morning, ate a ton of meat, and
came to the capital!
Delta, what are you doing in the capital?
I hunted a bunch! Boss man, wanna join?
Alpha told me to! Boss man, come hunt with me!
Yeah! Boss man, come hunt with me!
Bandits! Boss man, you love bandit hunting!
That's true. I do love bandit hunting.

Wait, didn't you have some business you had to deal
with here in the capital?
I assume Alpha called for you or something.

We can just go tomorrow, so go take care of your
business.

I'll be there at the dorm. Make sure you come
inconspicuously, though.

(...Delta reminds me of my pet John I had in my
previous life.)
The gorgeous room has two men in it.

Their personal guards were more formidable than
anticipated...

Although Garter is the president and Gettan is one of
his employees, one would never guess it from the way
they interact with each other.

The Clovers! If we deploy those elites handpicked
by you, Lord Gettan...

...it's as if we've already secured Mitsugoshi's
secrets!
